							"uid" : {
								"__type" : "uid",
								"uidString" : "Vmg1kPrRDQCA8Je8AqAYSw=="
							},
							"paragraphStyle" : {
								"__type" : "textStyle"
							},
							"string" : "The instance of {{gtClass:name=LcsGlobalCollectionSlot}} both defines the attributes of the slot and also is used to access the instance variable/slot. \n{{gtMethod:LxxPrototypeSystem>>persons}} and {{gtMethod:LxxPrototypeSystem>>persons:}} are examples of how the getter and setter are modified to redirect the accessing of the instance variable/slot to be via the slot definition instance."
						}
					]
				},
